Caesar,Ineverstoodonceremonies,
Yetnowtheyfrightme.Thereisonewithin,
Besidesthethingsthatwehaveheardandseen,
Recountsmosthorridsightsseenbythewatch.
Alionesshathwhelpedinthestreets;
