AndpitytothegeneralwrongofRome--
Asfiredrivesoutfire,sopitypity--
HathdonethisdeedonCaesar.Foryourpart,
Toyouourswordshaveleadenpoints,MarkAntony:
Ourarms,instrengthofmalice,andourhearts
Ofbrothers'temper,doreceiveyouin
Withallkindlove,goodthoughts,andreverence.
Yourvoiceshallbeasstrongasanyman's
Inthedisposingofnewdignities.
